version_description: Cleaned up the chords, pulled the lyrics together into longer lines.
I put chords in the second verse and put the baseline in.
Couldn't find the chords, or even a tab of this title track off one of Marc's albums, so I bought the sheet music and created a chord sheet. Far as I can tell, this is straight off the record.
One new Chord and one added C# Bass note. Repositioned Chords over lyrics. Included part of the song that was missing. Added [Intro, Verses and Choruses].
There are many versions but none seemed to match the sheet music. I am a piano player who would like the guitar to play along.
This TAB varies in it's chords and arrangement, from previous versions.

This song sounds better if you finger pick the verses and strum both the chorus and bridge. Finger picking pattern is bass note, 3rd string, 2nd string, bass note, 3rd string, 2nd string, 1st string, 3rd string (repeat).
